options.content:
# Datenbasis

Facebook: Reach

Instagram: Follower

YouTube: Videostarts von angemeldeten Usern. Bei YouTube angemeldet sind die User über ihr Google-Konto. Daten über nicht eingeloggte User bei YouTube liegen nicht vor.

Bei den Daten zu Alter und Geschlecht handelt es sich um eigene Angaben der User. Da nicht alle User diese Angaben machen, gibt es auch einen Anteil an Personen mit Status "Unbekannt".

Auch Personen, die nicht Fans/Follower sind, können die Inhalte der Profile sehen. Meta stellt die soziodemographischen Daten der Fans ab Mitte März 2024 nicht mehr zur Verfügung. Stattdessen kann bei Facebook nun die Reichweite ausgewertet werden, die Auskunft über die Personen gibt, die im ausgewählten Zeitraum den Inhalt eines Profils gesehen haben.

SELECT CASE $Zeitraum
WHEN 1 THEN Date($Jahr,1,31)
WHEN 2 THEN LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,2,1),MONTH)

WHEN 17 THEN Date($Jahr,6,30)
WHEN 18 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31)
WHEN 19 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31) END AS lastdayofzeitraum
), first_day_of_zeitraum AS (
SELECT CASE $Zeitraum
WHEN 1 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 2 THEN LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,2,1),MONTH)
WHEN 3 THEN Date($Jahr,3,1)
WHEN 4 THEN Date($Jahr,4,1)

WHEN 14 THEN Date($Jahr,4,1)
WHEN 15 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 16 THEN Date($Jahr,10,1)
WHEN 17 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 18 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 19 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1) END AS firstdayofzeitraum
)
SELECT CASE
WHEN firstdayofzeitraum > CURRENT_DATE() THEN "noch nicht abgeschlossen"
WHEN lastdayofzeitraum > CURRENT_DATE() THEN CONCAT( FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', firstdayofzeitraum), "-" , FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 2 DAY))) 
ELSE CONCAT( FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', firstdayofzeitraum), "-" , FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', lastdayofzeitraum)) END AS nutzungszeitraum
FROM last_day_of_zeitraum, first_day_of_zeitraum

WITH unscaled_values AS(
SELECT
EXTRACT(MONTH from time) as month,
CASE EXTRACT(MONTH from time)
  WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT('Jan. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 2 THEN CONCAT('Feb. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 3 THEN CONCAT('Mär. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 4 THEN CONCAT('Apr. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 5 THEN CONCAT('Mai. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 6 THEN CONCAT('Jun. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 7 THEN CONCAT('Jul. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 8 THEN CONCAT('Aug. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 9 THEN CONCAT('Sep. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 10 THEN CONCAT('Okt. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 11 THEN CONCAT('Nov. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT('Dez. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
END as Monat, 
 SUM(CASE WHEN ageBucket = '13-17' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS reach_13_17_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN ageBucket = '18-24' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS reach_18_24_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN ageBucket = '25-34' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS reach_25_34_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN ageBucket = '35-44' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS reach_35_44_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN ageBucket = '45-54' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS reach_45_54_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN ageBucket = '55-64' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS reach_55_64_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN ageBucket = '65+' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS reach_65_r,
 SUM(reach)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS total
FROM
  `Quintly.facebookInsightsByGenderAndAge`
WHERE 
 --EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr
 $Condition
 AND profileId = $facebookId 
GROUP BY
  Monat, month
ORDER BY 
month),
max_total_value AS (
  SELECT MAX(total) as total
  FROM unscaled_values
), scaled_values AS (
  SELECT month, Monat, 
  (reach_13_17_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_13_17_s,
  (reach_18_24_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_18_24_s,
  (reach_25_34_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_25_34_s,
  (reach_35_44_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_35_44_s,
  (reach_45_54_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_45_54_s,
  (reach_55_64_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_55_64_s,
  (reach_65_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_65_s,
  --unscaled_values.total
  FROM unscaled_values, max_total_value
  ORDER BY 
month
)
SELECT *, "${Skalierung}" as scailing, (max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7 as scailing_addition, max_total_value.total as total_s FROM unscaled_values, max_total_value
JOIN scaled_values
ON unscaled_values.month = scaled_values.month
ORDER BY unscaled_values.month

WITH unscaled_values AS(SELECT
EXTRACT(MONTH from time) as month,
CASE EXTRACT(MONTH from time)
  WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT('Jan. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 2 THEN CONCAT('Feb. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 3 THEN CONCAT('Mär. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 4 THEN CONCAT('Apr. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 5 THEN CONCAT('Mai. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 6 THEN CONCAT('Jun. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 7 THEN CONCAT('Jul. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 8 THEN CONCAT('Aug. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 9 THEN CONCAT('Sep. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 10 THEN CONCAT('Okt. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 11 THEN CONCAT('Nov. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT('Dez. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
END as Monat, 
 SUM(reach) as Gesamt,
 SUM(CASE WHEN gender = 'Unknown' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS unknown_reach_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN gender = 'Female' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS female_reach_r,
 SUM(CASE WHEN gender = 'Male' THEN reach ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) AS male_reach_r,
 SUM(reach)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) as total

FROM
  `Quintly.facebookInsightsByGenderAndAge`
WHERE 
 $Condition
 AND profileId = $facebookId 
GROUP BY
  Monat, month
ORDER BY 
month),
max_total_value AS (
  SELECT MAX(total) as total
  FROM unscaled_values
),
scaled_values AS (
  SELECT month, Monat, 
  (unknown_reach_r +(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/3) as unknown_reach_s,
  (female_reach_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/3) as female_reach_s,
  (male_reach_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/3) as male_reach_s,
  FROM unscaled_values, max_total_value
  ORDER BY 
month
)
SELECT *, "${Skalierung}" as scailing, (max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/3 as scailing_addition, max_total_value.total as total_s FROM unscaled_values, max_total_value
JOIN scaled_values
ON unscaled_values.month = scaled_values.month
ORDER BY unscaled_values.month

SELECT
ageBucket,
 ROUND(SUM(reach)/COUNT(DISTINCT time),3) AS total
FROM
  `Quintly.facebookInsightsByGenderAndAge`
WHERE 
 $Condition
 AND profileId = $facebookId 
 GROUP BY ageBucket
 ORDER BY CAST(LEFT(ageBucket,2) AS INT)

SELECT
CASE gender
WHEN "Male" THEN "Männlich"
WHEN "Female" THEN "Weiblich"
WHEN "Unknown" THEN "Unbekannt" END as gender,
 SUM(reach)/COUNT(DISTINCT time) as Gesamt

FROM
  `Quintly.facebookInsightsByGenderAndAge`
WHERE 
 --EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr
 $Condition

WITH last_day_of_zeitraum AS (
SELECT CASE $Zeitraum
WHEN 1 THEN Date($Jahr,1,31)
WHEN 2 THEN LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,2,1),MONTH)
WHEN 3 THEN Date($Jahr,3,31)
WHEN 4 THEN Date($Jahr,4,30)
WHEN 5 THEN Date($Jahr,5,31)
WHEN 6 THEN Date($Jahr,6,30)
WHEN 7 THEN Date($Jahr,7,31)
WHEN 8 THEN Date($Jahr,8,31)
WHEN 9 THEN Date($Jahr,9,30)
WHEN 10 THEN Date($Jahr,10,31)
WHEN 11 THEN Date($Jahr,11,30)
WHEN 12 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31)
WHEN 13 THEN Date($Jahr,3,31)
WHEN 14 THEN Date($Jahr,6,30)
WHEN 15 THEN Date($Jahr,9,30)
WHEN 16 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31)
WHEN 17 THEN Date($Jahr,6,30)
WHEN 18 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31)
WHEN 19 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31) END AS lastdayofzeitraum
), first_day_of_zeitraum AS (
SELECT CASE $Zeitraum
WHEN 1 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 2 THEN LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,2,1),MONTH)
WHEN 3 THEN Date($Jahr,3,1)
WHEN 4 THEN Date($Jahr,4,1)
WHEN 5 THEN Date($Jahr,5,1)
WHEN 6 THEN Date($Jahr,6,1)
WHEN 7 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 8 THEN Date($Jahr,8,1)

WHEN 10 THEN Date($Jahr,10,1)

WHEN 12 THEN Date($Jahr,12,1)
WHEN 13 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 14 THEN Date($Jahr,4,1)
WHEN 15 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 16 THEN Date($Jahr,10,1)
WHEN 17 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 18 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 19 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1) END AS firstdayofzeitraum
)
--SELECT * FROM last_day_of_zeitraum
SELECT CASE
WHEN firstdayofzeitraum > CURRENT_DATE() THEN "noch nicht abgeschlossen"
WHEN lastdayofzeitraum > CURRENT_DATE() THEN  FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 4 DAY))
ELSE  FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', lastdayofzeitraum) END AS stichtag
FROM last_day_of_zeitraum, first_day_of_zeitraum

WITH WeightedAverages AS (
  SELECT
    CASE SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.id, STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.id, '-') + 1)
      WHEN "13-17" THEN 15
      WHEN "18-24" THEN 21
      WHEN "25-34" THEN 29.5
      WHEN "35-44" THEN 39.5
      WHEN "45-54" THEN 49.5
      WHEN "55-64" THEN 59.5
      ELSE 69.5
    END AS mid_age,
    SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.followers) AS age_bucket_followers
  FROM
    `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsights`,
    UNNEST(audienceGenderAndAge) AS audienceGenderAndAge
  WHERE $Condition 
  AND profileId = $instagramId 
  GROUP BY
    audienceGenderAndAge.id
)

SELECT 
  SUM(mid_age * age_bucket_followers / (SELECT SUM(age_bucket_followers) FROM WeightedAverages)) as average_age
FROM
  WeightedAverages

WITH UniqueData AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
      audienceGenderAndAge.id AS id,
      audienceGenderAndAge.name AS name,
      audienceGenderAndAge.followers AS followers,
      last_update,
      profileId
    FROM
      `Quintly.instagramInsights`,
      UNNEST(audienceGenderAndAge) AS audienceGenderAndAge
    WHERE $FollowerCondition
)

SELECT
  SUBSTR(UniqueData.id, STRPOS(UniqueData.id, '-') + 1) AS ageBucket,
  ROUND(SUM(UniqueData.followers)/1000,1) as Gesamt,
  ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(UniqueData.name,'male') AND NOT CONTAINS_SUBSTR(UniqueData.name,'female') THEN UniqueData.followers ELSE 0 END)/1000,1) AS male_total_followers,
  ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(UniqueData.name,'female') THEN UniqueData.followers ELSE 0 END)/1000,1) AS female_total_followers,
  ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(UniqueData.name,'unknown') THEN UniqueData.followers ELSE 0 END)/1000,1) AS unknown_total_followers
FROM UniqueData
WHERE last_update = (SELECT MAX(last_update) from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsights` WHERE $FollowerCondition and profileId = $instagramId)
AND UniqueData.profileId = $instagramId
GROUP BY ageBucket
ORDER BY CAST(LEFT(ageBucket,2) AS INT) DESC

panels.title: Instagram Follower nach Geschlecht und Alter in Tausend

targets.rawSql:
WITH UniqueData AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
      audienceGenderAndAge.id AS id,
      audienceGenderAndAge.name AS name,
      audienceGenderAndAge.followers AS followers,
      last_update,
      profileId
    FROM
      `Quintly.instagramInsights`,
      UNNEST(audienceGenderAndAge) AS audienceGenderAndAge
    WHERE $FollowerCondition
)

, TotalFollowers AS (
  SELECT
    SUM(followers) as total_followers
  FROM UniqueData
  WHERE last_update = (SELECT MAX(last_update) from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsights` WHERE $FollowerCondition and profileId = $instagramId)
  AND profileId = $instagramId
)

SELECT
  ageBucket,
  Gesamt*100 / 1 AS relative_percentage
FROM (
  SELECT
    SUBSTR(id, STRPOS(id, '-') + 1) AS ageBucket,
    SUM(followers) as Gesamt
  FROM UniqueData
  WHERE last_update = (SELECT MAX(last_update) from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsights` WHERE $FollowerCondition and profileId = $instagramId)
  AND profileId = $instagramId
  GROUP BY ageBucket
) subquery
CROSS JOIN TotalFollowers
ORDER BY ageBucket;

WITH UniqueData AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
      audienceGenderAndAge.id AS id,
      audienceGenderAndAge.name AS name,
      audienceGenderAndAge.followers AS followers,
      last_update,
      profileId
    FROM
      `Quintly.instagramInsights`,
      UNNEST(audienceGenderAndAge) AS audienceGenderAndAge
    WHERE $FollowerCondition
)

SELECT
  CASE 
    WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'male') AND NOT CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'female') THEN 'Männlich'
    WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'female') THEN 'Weiblich'
    ELSE 'Unbekannt'
  END AS gender,
  SUM(followers) / 1 as percentage
FROM UniqueData
WHERE last_update = (SELECT MAX(last_update) from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsights` WHERE $FollowerCondition and profileId = $instagramId)
AND profileId = $instagramId
GROUP BY gender;

WITH UniqueData AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
      audienceGenderAndAge.id AS id,
      audienceGenderAndAge.name AS name,
      audienceGenderAndAge.followers AS followers,
      last_update,
      profileId
    FROM
      `Quintly.instagramInsights`,
      UNNEST(audienceGenderAndAge) AS audienceGenderAndAge
    WHERE $FollowerCondition
)

SELECT
  CASE 
    WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'male') AND NOT CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'female') THEN 'Männlich'
    WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'female') THEN 'Weiblich'
  END AS gender,
  SUM(followers) / 1 as percentage --(SELECT SUM(followers) FROM UniqueData WHERE last_update = (SELECT MAX(last_update) from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsights` WHERE $FollowerCondition and profileId = $instagramId  AND NOT CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'unknown') ) AND profileId = $instagramId) AS percentage
FROM UniqueData
WHERE last_update = (SELECT MAX(last_update) from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsights` WHERE $FollowerCondition and profileId = $instagramId)
AND profileId = $instagramId
AND NOT CONTAINS_SUBSTR(name,'unknown') -- Diese Bedingung ignoriert den "Unbekannt" Anteil
GROUP BY gender;

SELECT SUM(Gesamt)

FROM
(SELECT ageBucket, (male_total_followers + female_total_followers + unknown_total_followers) as Gesamt, male_total_followers , female_total_followers , unknown_total_followers FROM( SELECT
  SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) AS ageBucket,
  SUM(CASE WHEN NOT(CONTAINS_SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.gender,'female')) AND CONTAINS_SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.gender,'male')  THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) AS male_total_followers,
  SUM(CASE WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.gender,'female')THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) AS female_total_followers,
  SUM(CASE WHEN CONTAINS_SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.gender,'genderUserSpecified') THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) AS unknown_total_followers

FROM
  `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtubeAnalytics`,
  UNNEST(viewsByAgeAndGender) AS audienceGenderAndAge
WHERE
  $Condition 
  AND profileId = $youtubeId 
GROUP BY
  ageBucket
  ORDER BY ageBucket)
)

SELECT SUM(average_per_age) as average_age
FROM(
SELECT
  CASE TRIM(SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')))
  WHEN "13-17" THEN 15 *  ROUND(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value) / SUM(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value)) OVER(), 2)
  WHEN "18-24" THEN 21 *  ROUND(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value) / SUM(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value)) OVER(), 2)
  WHEN "25-34" THEN 29.5 *  ROUND(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value) / SUM(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value)) OVER(), 2)
  WHEN "35-44" THEN 39.5 *  ROUND(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value) / SUM(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value)) OVER(), 2)
  WHEN "45-54" THEN 49.5 *  ROUND(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value) / SUM(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value)) OVER(), 2)
  WHEN "55-64" THEN 59.5 *  ROUND(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value) / SUM(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value)) OVER(), 2)
  ELSE 69.5 * ROUND(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value) / SUM(SUM(audienceGenderAndAge.value)) OVER(), 2)
  END as average_per_age
FROM
  `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtubeAnalytics`,
  UNNEST(viewsByAgeAndGender) AS audienceGenderAndAge
  WHERE $Condition  
  AND profileId = $youtubeId 
GROUP BY
  audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName

)

WITH unscaled_values AS (SELECT
EXTRACT(MONTH from time) as month,
CASE EXTRACT(MONTH from time)
  WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT('Jan. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 2 THEN CONCAT('Feb. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 3 THEN CONCAT('Mär. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 4 THEN CONCAT('Apr. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 5 THEN CONCAT('Mai. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 6 THEN CONCAT('Jun. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 7 THEN CONCAT('Jul. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 8 THEN CONCAT('Aug. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 9 THEN CONCAT('Sep. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 10 THEN CONCAT('Okt. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 11 THEN CONCAT('Nov. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
  WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT('Dez. ', SUBSTRING("$Jahr",3,3))
END as Monat, 
SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) = '13-17 ' THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) as reach_13_17_r,
SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) = '18-24 ' THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) as reach_18_24_r,
SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) = '25-34 ' THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) as reach_25_34_r,
SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) = '35-44 ' THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) as reach_35_44_r,
SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) = '45-54 ' THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) as reach_45_54_r,
SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) = '55-64 ' THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) as reach_55_64_r,
SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName,0,  STRPOS(audienceGenderAndAge.ageGroupName, ' ')) = '65+ ' THEN audienceGenderAndAge.value ELSE 0 END) as reach_65_r,
SUM(IFNULL(audienceGenderAndAge.value,0)) AS total
  FROM
  `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtubeAnalytics`,
  UNNEST(viewsByAgeAndGender) AS audienceGenderAndAge
    WHERE
  $Condition 
  AND profileId = $youtubeId 
  GROUP BY Monat,month
  ORDER BY month),
  max_total_value AS (
  SELECT MAX(total) as total
  FROM unscaled_values
), scaled_values AS (
  SELECT month, Monat, 
  (reach_13_17_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_13_17_s,
  (reach_18_24_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_18_24_s,
  (reach_25_34_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_25_34_s,
  (reach_35_44_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_35_44_s,
  (reach_45_54_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_45_54_s,
  (reach_55_64_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_55_64_s,
  (reach_65_r+(max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7) as reach_65_s,
  --unscaled_values.total
  FROM unscaled_values, max_total_value
  ORDER BY 
month
)
SELECT *, "${Skalierung}" as scailing, (max_total_value.total-unscaled_values.total)/7 as scailing_addition, max_total_value.total as total_s FROM unscaled_values, max_total_value
JOIN scaled_values
ON unscaled_values.month = scaled_values.month
ORDER BY unscaled_values.month

SELECT a.LRA
FROM (
  SELECT DISTINCT LRA FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles`
) as a
ORDER BY (
  CASE
    WHEN REGEXP_CONTAINS(LOWER("${__user.email}"), LOWER(a.LRA))
    THEN 1
    ELSE 0
  END
) DESC

SELECT a.profile 
FROM 
(SELECT profile FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles` WHERE LRA = '$LRA' AND (facebookID > 0 OR instagramID >0 or youtubeID > 0)) as a,
(SELECT  Profil_FB FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.default-settings` WHERE LRA = '$LRA') as b
ORDER BY( 
CASE WHEN a.profile = b.Profil_FB THEN 1
ELSE 2
END
), a.profile ASC

SELECT 
CASE 
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 13 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 03, 31) THEN "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 1 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 3 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 13 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 2 DAY) AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 1 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 3 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 14 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 06, 30) THEN "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 4 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 6 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 14 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 2 DAY) AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 4 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 6 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"

    WHEN $Zeitraum = 15 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 09, 30) THEN "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 7 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 9 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 15 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 2 DAY) AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 7 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 9 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"

    WHEN $Zeitraum = 16 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 12, 31) THEN "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 10 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 12 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 16 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 2 DAY) AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 10 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 12 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"

    WHEN $Zeitraum = 17 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 06, 30) THEN "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 1 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 6 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 17 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 2 DAY) AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 1 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 6 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"

    WHEN $Zeitraum = 18 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 12, 31) THEN "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 7 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 12 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 18 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 2 DAY) AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 7 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 12 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"

    WHEN $Zeitraum = 19 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 12, 31) THEN "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 1 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 12 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 19 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 2 DAY) AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) >= 1 AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) <= 12 AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr"
    ELSE "EXTRACT(MONTH from time) = $Zeitraum AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr" 
END;

SELECT CASE $Zeitraum
WHEN 1 THEN concat("Januar ",$Jahr)
WHEN 2 THEN concat("Februar",$Jahr)
WHEN 3 THEN concat("März ", $Jahr)

SELECT CASE $Zeitraum
WHEN 1 THEN CAST(Date($Jahr,1,31) AS STRING)
WHEN 2 THEN CAST(LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,2,1),MONTH) AS STRING)
WHEN 3 THEN CAST(Date($Jahr,1,31) AS STRING)

WHEN 18 THEN CAST(Date($Jahr,12,31) AS STRING)
WHEN 19 THEN CAST(Date($Jahr,12,31) AS STRING) END

SELECT 
CASE 
    -- 1.Quartal
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 13 AND CURRENT_DATE() > LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,03,01)) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,03,01))"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 13 AND CURRENT_DATE() >= DATE($Jahr,03,05) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 13 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) =  LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,03,01))"

    -- 2.Quartal
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 14 AND CURRENT_DATE() > LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,06,01)) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,06,01))"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 14 AND CURRENT_DATE() >= DATE($Jahr,04,05) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 14 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,06,01))"

    -- 3.Quartal
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 15 AND CURRENT_DATE() > LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,09,01)) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,09,01))"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 15 AND CURRENT_DATE() >= DATE($Jahr,07,05) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 15 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01))"

    -- 4.Quartal
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 16 AND CURRENT_DATE() > LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01)) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01))"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 16 AND CURRENT_DATE() >= DATE($Jahr,10,05) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 16 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01))"

    --1.Halbjahr
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 17 AND CURRENT_DATE() > LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,06,01)) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,06,01))"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 17 AND CURRENT_DATE() < DATE($Jahr,06,06) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 17 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"

    -- 2.Halbjahr
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 18 AND CURRENT_DATE() > LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01)) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01))"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 18 AND CURRENT_DATE() >= DATE($Jahr,12,05) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 18 THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01))"

    -- Jahr
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 19 AND $Jahr >= EXTRACT(YEAR from CURRENT_DATE()) AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 19 AND $Jahr >= EXTRACT(YEAR from CURRENT_DATE()) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
    WHEN $Zeitraum = 19 AND $Jahr <= EXTRACT(YEAR from CURRENT_DATE()) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,12,01))"

    -- All other months
    ELSE 
        CASE
            WHEN CURRENT_DATE() <= LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,$Zeitraum,01)) AND CURRENT_DATE() >= DATE($Jahr,$Zeitraum,05) THEN "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 4 DAY)"
            ELSE "EXTRACT(DATE from time) = LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,$Zeitraum,01))"
        END
END;

WHEN 16 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31)
WHEN 17 THEN Date($Jahr,6,30)
WHEN 18 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31)
WHEN 19 THEN Date($Jahr,12,31) END AS lastdayofzeitraum
), first_day_of_zeitraum AS (
SELECT CASE $Zeitraum
WHEN 1 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 2 THEN LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,2,1),MONTH)
WHEN 3 THEN Date($Jahr,3,1)
WHEN 4 THEN Date($Jahr,4,1)
WHEN 5 THEN Date($Jahr,5,1)
WHEN 6 THEN Date($Jahr,6,1)
WHEN 7 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 8 THEN Date($Jahr,8,1)
WHEN 9 THEN Date($Jahr,9,1)
WHEN 10 THEN Date($Jahr,10,1)
WHEN 11 THEN Date($Jahr,11,1)
WHEN 12 THEN Date($Jahr,12,1)
WHEN 13 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 14 THEN Date($Jahr,4,1)
WHEN 15 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 16 THEN Date($Jahr,10,1)
WHEN 17 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1)
WHEN 18 THEN Date($Jahr,7,1)
WHEN 19 THEN Date($Jahr,1,1) END AS firstdayofzeitraum
)
--SELECT * FROM last_day_of_zeitraum
SELECT CASE
WHEN firstdayofzeitraum > CURRENT_DATE() THEN "noch nicht abgeschlossen"
WHEN lastdayofzeitraum > CURRENT_DATE() THEN  FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 4 DAY))
ELSE  FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', lastdayofzeitraum) END AS stichtag
FROM last_day_of_zeitraum, first_day_of_zeitraum
